<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>台股動能儀表板 — 歷史存檔</title>
<link rel="icon" href="../favicon.ico">
<style>
  :root { --bg:#0d1117; --surface:#161b22; --border:#30363d; --text:#e6edf3; --muted:#8b949e; --blue:#58a6ff; }
  * { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
  body { background:var(--bg); color:var(--text); font-family:'Segoe UI',-apple-system,sans-serif;
         font-size:14px; padding:32px 16px; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; }
  h1 { font-size:20px; color:var(--blue); font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .meta { color:var(--muted); font-size:12px; margin-bottom:28px; }
  .archive-list { border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden; }
  .archive-item {
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    background:var(--surface); padding:12px 16px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .archive-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .archive-item:hover { background:#1c2128; }
  .date-label { font-weight:600; color:var(--text); }
  .weekday { color:var(--muted); font-size:12px; margin-left:8px; }
  .open-btn {
    background:none; border:1px solid var(--blue); color:var(--blue);
    font-size:12px; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:4px; cursor:pointer;
    text-decoration:none;
  }
  .open-btn:hover { background:rgba(88,166,255,0.1); }
  .empty { padding:32px; text-align:center; color:var(--muted); font-style:italic; }
  .footer { margin-top:24px; font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); text-align:center; }
  .footer a { color:var(--blue); text-decoration:none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>📊 台股動能作戰儀表板 — 歷史存檔</h1>
<div class="meta">共 {{ archives | length }} 筆存檔 ｜ 最新至最舊排列</div>

{% if archives %}
<div class="archive-list">
  {% for item in archives %}
  <div class="archive-item">
    <div>
      <span class="date-label">{{ item.date }}</span>
      <span class="weekday">{{ item.weekday }}</span>
    </div>
    <a class="open-btn" href="{{ item.filename }}">開啟 →</a>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
<div class="archive-list"><div class="empty">尚無存檔記錄</div></div>
{% endif %}

<div class="footer">
  <a href="../index.html">← 返回最新儀表板</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
